cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

This paper deals with computer vision and image processing, specifically in the context of predicting the environment from a single image. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also deals with modeling the statistics of environments and material properties, which could fall under cs.GR (Graphics) or cs.MM (Multimedia). The proposed learning-based approach involves predicting the environment from reflectance maps, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning).
